      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Iſdohmajcet weenu Pa-\ndohnu/ bet tas taps iſnihzi-\nnahts/ runnajt weenu Wahrdü/\nbet tas ne paſtahwehs/ jo (ſcheic)\nirr * Immanuel.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta irr tas KUNGS\nus man runnajs. Kad wiſch\n(mannu) Rohku fitprinaja / un\nirr manni mahzijs / ka man ne\nbuhs eet us to Zeltu ſcho Lau-\nſchu/ un ſazztis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums ne buhs ſazztis:\nDerriha/us wiſeem us ko ſchee\nLaudis jatta: Derriha. Un ne\nbihſteetees/ ta ka wiſſti bihſtahs/\nun ka wiſſti baiiojahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To KUNGU Zebaot to\nbuhs jums ſwehtiht/ un tas lai\nter juhjn Bihjaſchana/ un tas lai\nter juhsn Bailiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs wiſch jums\npar Sweihtſchanu/ bet par Pee-\n8- durchanas Akmini / un par\nPeedanſſchanas Akmini teem\ndiwi Iſraëta Naimneemi / par\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un dauds ſtarp teem pee-\ndauiſeeß/ un krittihs / un taps\ntadausiti/ un eetihſtiti / un fa-\nguhſtiti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Gafeen to Leezibu / aiſ-\nſehgele to Bauſlibu ſtarp man-\nneim Mahzekkeim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz zerreju es us to\nKUNGU/ kas ſawu Waignu irr\napſlehpiß no Jehkaba Naimma/\nbet es gaidiſchu us winzu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redsi/ es un tee Behrni/\nfo tas KUNGGS man dewiſ irr/\npar Sihmehni un par Brihnu-\nmeem eeſch Iſraëta no ta KUN-\nGA Zebaot/ kas us Zianas Kal-\nnu mahjo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee nu us jums ſaz-\nzihß: Waizajeet tohs Paredſe-\ntajus un Sihmes-Zeenitajus/\nkas fehrz/ un ar neprattigeim\nWahrdeem runna/ ( tad ſak-\nkaſt:) Neggi buhs teem Eaudim\nſawu Deewu wazaht? buhs tad\npreekſch teem kas dsil wo Mirru-\nſchus wazaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz tahs Bauſlibas un\npehz tahs Leezibas/ ja tee nerun-\nnahß pehz ſcho Wahrdü / tad\nteem tas Auſeklis ne aufihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tee ere zauri/ ſohti\napbehdiuati un iſfaltuſchi. Un\nkad kas buhs iſſalzis/ tad wiſch\napduſmoſeeß/ un lahdehs ſawu\nKehninu un ſawu Deewu us\naugſchu ſkattiſanceeß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiſch to Semmi\nuſluhkohß/ tad raugi/ buhs Beh-\ndas\n"
